snippet.title: The Yoshi Garden - Showcase and Release Video
snippet.description:
Grow, Care for and play with your Yoshis! Breed your favourite Yoshi color and plot your Yoshis against each other in competitions!
Subscribe for more Retro Mods!
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/Kazestuff
🎥 https://www.twitch.tv/kazesm64
🐦 https://twitter.com/KazeEmanuar


Patch the downloaded file on your SUPER MARIO 64 (U) [!].Z64  rom!
Download: https://mega.nz/file/vawnxb7Z#Uz69w6U4wzBM8iYYv1mA_u0mpwrxQ9R8Id_1sjtQxyA
Patcher (patch onto the SM64 US.z64 ROM!!): https://hack64.net/tools/patcher.php

The OST for this was composed by lezg_g/zerovolt0v. Check him out on soundcloud! https://soundcloud.com/zerovolt0v
The release trailer was edited by Ryoyo! https://twitter.com/doozydev
